{"tid":434783,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[半直播]盧恩(RUNE)個性複合符文設計","createTime":"2017-10-13T15:32:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-15T17:14:59.000Z","uid":150595,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9e9425979bbfe6ee9a67b622dffaca5452367c51","tid":434783,"uid":150595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T15:32:23.000Z","msg":"大家好﹗我係秋嵐<br />\n為左慶祝成功無穿無爛渡過本年度最後一個黑色星期五(藉口)<br />\n開個POST畫下圖案。<br />\n<br />\n利申︰我唔係學左好耐，所以畫得唔靚都粗粗地接受我GE好意啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/13/232045_f9e01550815a51be720a93d444017dc1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F13%2F232045_f9e01550815a51be720a93d444017dc1.jpg&h=404b407b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/13/232058_506b2ffa342f8306918c48e67a724e0d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F13%2F232058_506b2ffa342f8306918c48e67a724e0d.jpg&h=6d3cca1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n若果你都有興趣就留低2選1<br />\n1. 你個英文名GE字頭<br />\n例如︰CHAN TAI MAN，咁就係CTM<br />\n幕容呀姑蘇呀果D咪4個字母囉。<br />\n2. 任何唔係粗口/侮辱/犯法GE 4字母以內單字<br />\n舉個例子(呢個POST唔會用電腦畫架)︰<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/13/232051_c05dafaf7aa665803b7e35698bc02b48.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F13%2F232051_c05dafaf7aa665803b7e35698bc02b48.jpg&h=cbd4f157&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">頭5個一定會手畫出來俾你，之後果D....係咪真係有人要都唔知。</span><br />\n<br />\n我FACEBOOK(@indigo.aki)會開直播架，有興趣可以來睇，無人來就開到12點~<br />\n(不過唔一定係播住畫O野~哈哈哈~可能係睇片架咋~入唔入來自己決定啦。)<br />\n<br />\n覺得好GE記得LIKE、SHARE、FOLLOW~"},{"pid":"b1cdd4a73b2f23885914ced5de9ce348d526ee97","tid":434783,"uid":150595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T16:18:32.000Z","msg":"半個鐘都無發巿添~<br />\n直播要CLOSE啦~<br />\n字可以照留呀~頭5個會畫返貼上來架~"},{"pid":"1